room_title: Escape room "The Butcher Shop" by C & C Xscape Rooms in Winona
room_description: Your hiking in a remote area of the Appalachian Mountains. All of the sudden, things go black! You wake up with a huge headache and blurry vision. Looking around you notice your in what looks like a backwoods butcher shop. You gasp in horror as you read the sign above the counter that reads "best human parts"! WHAT? You must find your way out of the shop in one hour before the butcher returns!
